# 21. 25時、ナイトコードで。

Mizuki: Oh, there she is! Hey, over here!
Kanade: Sorry, I'm late.
Ena: You're fine. Yuki still isn't here yet.
Mizuki: She messaged me saying her class ran late, but she should be here soon.
Kanade: I see.
Ena: I know we just saw each other yesterday, but this is still our first time meeting up in the real world. It feels a little weird.
Mizuki: Yeah, I'm not sure meeting in the other world like that counts. I finally feel like I can be sure you two actually exist. It's so strange.
Ena: You look at all the pictures I post, don't you?
Mizuki: Well yeah, but you just seem different now that I'm actually meeting the real you in person.
Ena: Oh? In what way?
Mizuki: Let's see. For starters, now I know for sure that you're always using filters when you post your pictures♪
Ena: The hell?!
???: Sorry, I'm late.
Kanade: Oh...
Ena: Yuki...
Mizuki: No problem! We haven't been here long! We still haven't even ordered.
???: I see. That's good.
???: May I sit here?
Kanade: Oh, sure.
Mizuki: Alright then. Let's start with a round of introductions! My name is Mizuki Akiyama. Call me Mizuki♪ Okay, Enanan, your turn.
Ena: Fine...
Ena: I'm Ena Shinonome. It feels a little weird introducing myself again.
Mizuki: Oh, I guess we never really did use your real name after you told us. I'll make sure to start using it now♪
Mizuki: Who's next?
Kanade: I'm Kanade Yoisaki.
Kanade: What about you, Yuki?
???: .....
???: I'm Mafuyu Asahina.
Kanade: Mafuyu...
Kanade: Do you use the characters for midwinter? It makes sense why you chose Yuki since it means snow.
Mafuyu: .....
Kanade: It's nice to finally meet you, Mafuyu.
Mafuyu: Same.
Mafuyu: I'm sorry for causing so much trouble.
Ena: Hey, do you actually feel bad for what you did?
Mafuyu: I'm not sure. I don't really know myself.
Ena: Seriously? You're the one who caused this whole mess. The least you could do is feel sorry.
Mafuyu: I think I do.
Ena: You're not going to be like this from now on, are you?
Mizuki: Oh, I know! Let's order! My tummy's a-rumbling! What are you getting, Ena?
Ena: I had a late lunch, so I'm just getting some cheesecake and an iced tea.
Mafuyu: I'm okay with whatever.
Mizuki: Hey, hey! You gotta decide for yourself, Mafuyu!
Mafuyu: What are you getting, K?
Kanade: I think I'll go with the wonton noodles and an oolong tea.
Mafuyu: I'll get that too, then.
Mizuki: Good, we're all decided. Let's order and make a toast!
Ena: A toast? For what?
Mizuki: For the first official offline meeting of N25, of course! That's the whole reason I asked everyone here today♪
Mizuki: Oh, are you two okay with this level of energy?
Kanade: Yeah. I don't dislike it.
Mafuyu: Same.
Shop Clerk: Sorry for the wait. Here's your order.
Mizuki: Oh, thank you♪ Let's see. Kanade and Mafuyu ordered oolong tea and Ena had the iced tea. Great, everyone has their drinks.
Mizuki: Alright, let the first official offline meeting of N25 begin! Cheers!
Ena: Cheers... You really are way too excited.
Kanade: I think that's probably good for today.
Kanade: I should get some sleep.
Kanade: Huh? A Nightcord notification?
Kanade: A DM from Mafuyu?
Mafuyu: <Are you still up?>
Kanade: <Yeah, I'm up.>
Mafuyu: <I listened to the song you wrote.>
Kanade: So she listened to it.
Kanade: <What did you think?>
Kanade: She's not responding. I wonder if she fell asleep.
Kanade: .....
Kanade: (My songs still aren't enough for Mafuyu. But someday...)
Kanade: Hm?
Mafuyu: <Kanade...>
Mafuyu: <Thank you for finding me.>
Kanade: !!
Kanade: Heh.
Kanade: <Mafuyu...>
Kanade: <Thank you as well.>
Miku: I'm glad you found each other.
